TaxPay App
Overview
TaxPay is a web application designed to streamline the tax payment process for startup companies and small businesses in Denmark. 
Our goal is to simplify the often complex and time-consuming task of managing tax obligations, 
ensuring compliance with local regulations while saving users valuable time and resources.

Features
User-Friendly Interface: Intuitive design that simplifies navigation and makes tax management easy for users.

Tax Calculation: Automatically calculate tax liabilities based on user inputs, ensuring accurate and timely submissions.

Payment Reminders: Automated notifications remind users of upcoming tax deadlines to prevent late payments.

Historical Data: Keep track of past tax payments and financial summaries for better financial planning and analysis.

Secure Payment Gateway: Integrates with secure payment platforms for safe transactions.

Technologies Used
Frontend: React.js for building a responsive user interface.
Backend: C# and .NET for handling API requests and processing data.
Database: SQL Server or a suitable database of choice for storing user data and transaction records.
Charting: Chart.js for visualizing financial data and trends.

Usage
Navigate to http://localhost:3000 in your web browser.
Create an account or log in.
Access the dashboard to view financial summaries and manage tax payments.
Use the reporting feature to generate tax reports.
